title: Clinton seeking to organize Latino voters ahead of primaries
text: > Florida Clinton seeking to organize Latino voters ahead of primaries FILE - In this June 18, 2015 file photo, Democratic presidential candidate Hillary Rodham Clinton speaks at the National Association of Latino Elected and Appointed Officials in Las Vegas. Clinton's campaign is planning a major push to organize Latino voters ahead of the Nevada caucuses and early primary contests in Texas, Florida and Colorado, all with an eye toward connecting with Hispanics in the 2016 election. (AP Photo/David Becker)
